      <scopecontent id="aspace_04d1d6c8464eb3cd2e28af7fa9a7ce2c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of administrative and historical files documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Department of Spanish and Portuguese. Included are records of the department Advisory Committee.</p>  
